### 列出 Prompt 定义
GET http://localhost:8080/api/prompts

### 获取 database.agent user 模板
GET http://localhost:8080/api/prompts/database.agent/user

### 创建新版本
POST http://localhost:8080/api/prompts/database.agent/user/versions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "用户问题：{{question}}\n\nSchema：\n{{schema}}\n\n索引：\n{{indexes}}\n\n请分析。"
}

### 设为生效版本
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/prompts/database.agent/user/active
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "version": 2
}

### 预览渲染
POST http://localhost:8080/api/prompts/render
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "key": "database.agent",
  "type": "user",
  "variables": {
    "question": "为什么慢？",
    "schema": "orders(id)",
    "indexes": "idx_orders_id"
  }
}

### 列出版本历史
GET http://localhost:8080/api/prompts/database.agent/user/versions

### 删除非生效版本
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/prompts/database.agent/user/versions/1
